Package matrix.vui

Interface Summary
DialogClient This interface is used to notify clients of certain events occurring in the life of a dialog.
DragAndDropFrame Frames that want to support drag and drop must implement this interface.
DragAndDropTarget Implement this interface to allow objects to be dropped on you.
DragAndDropViewerClient This interface is used to notify clients of certain events occurring in the life of a Viewer that supports drag and drop.
IndentedViewerClient This interface is used to notify clients of certain events occurring in the life of an IndentedViewer.
ListerClient This interface is used to notify clients of certain events occurring in the life of a Lister.
TipProvider This interface is the basis for providing helpful tips to the user of our interface.
TreeTableModel TreeTableModel is the model used by a JTreeTable.
TreeViewer Interface definition for TreeViewer
Viewer Interface definition for Viewer
ViewerClient This interface is used to notify clients of certain events occurring in the life of a Viewer.
